#. Tag: title
#: menu-commands.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Menu"
msgstr "Menyn Arkiv"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; <keycap>F4</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Text File...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; <keycap>F4</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ny textfil...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new text file in the current folder, unless another folder is "
"specified. The new file is opened for editing after it is created."
msgstr ""
"Skapar en ny textfil i aktuell katalog, om inte en annan katalog har "
"angivits. Den nya filen öppnas för redigering efter den har skapats."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F7</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>New Folder</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F7</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Ny katalog</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creates a new folder in the current folder."
msgstr "Skapar en ny katalog i den aktuella katalogen."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Alt;&Ctrl; <keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Symlink...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Alt;&Ctrl; <keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ny symbolisk "
"länk...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creates a symbolic link to the currently selected file."
msgstr "Skapar en symbolisk länk till filen som för närvarande är markerad."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F3</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>View File</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F3</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Granska fil</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the currently selected file for <link linkend=\"kredit\">viewing</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Öppnar filen som för närvarande är markerad för <link linkend=\"kredit"
"\">granskning</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F4</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Edit File</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F4</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Redigera fil</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the currently selected file for <link linkend=\"kredit\">editing</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Öppnar filen som för närvarande är markerad för <link linkend=\"kredit"
"\">redigering</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F5</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Copy to other panel</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F5</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Kopiera till andra panelen</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy the currently selected files or folders to the other panel."
msgstr ""
"Kopiera filerna eller katalogerna som för närvarande är markerade till den "
"andra panelen."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F6</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Move</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F6</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Flytta</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a dialog to <link linkend=\"copying\">move</link> the currently "
"selected files or folders to a specified location."
msgstr ""
"Öppnar en dialogruta för att <link linkend=\"copying\">flytta</link> filerna "
"eller katalogerna som för närvarande är markerade till en angiven plats."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>P</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pack...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>P</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Packa...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a <link linkend=\"pack-archive\">new archive</link> of all the "
"selected files and folders in the active panel."
msgstr ""
"Skapar en <link linkend=\"pack-archive\">ny arkivfil</link> med alla "
"markerade filer och kataloger i den aktiva panelen."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>U</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Unpack...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>U</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Packa upp...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"unpacking-archives\">Unpacks</link> all the selected files "
"in the active panel."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"unpacking-archives\">Packar upp</link> alla filer markerade "
"i den aktiva panelen."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Test Archive</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Testa arkivfil</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"test-archive\">Tests archive</link> for corruption."
msgstr "<link linkend=\"test-archive\">Testar arkivfilen</link> för skador."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Compare by Content...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Jämför innehåll...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compares two current files by content - one from each panel via an external "
"graphical diff utility. By default &kompare; is used, but you can also use "
"&eg; <ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/xxdiff/\"><application>xxdiff</"
"application></ulink> or <ulink url=\"https://apps.kde.org/"
"kdiff3\"><application>KDiff3</application></ulink> , change it in the <link "
"linkend=\"konfig-dependencies\">Konfigurator Dependencies page</link>."
msgstr ""
"Jämför två aktuella filer enligt innehåll, en från varje panel, med ett "
"externt grafiskt jämförelseverktyg. Normalt används &kompare;, men du kan t."
"ex. också använda <ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/xxdiff/"
"\"><application>xxdiff</application></ulink> eller <ulink url=\"https://apps."
"kde.org/kdiff3\"><application>KDiff3</application></ulink>, ändra det på "
"sidan <link linkend=\"konfig-dependencies\">Beroenden</link> i Konfigurator."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; <keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Multi Rename...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; <keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mängdnamnbyte...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu option starts <ulink url=\"hhttps://apps.kde.org/krename"
"\"><application>Krename</application></ulink>, a very powerful external "
"batch renamer."
msgstr ""
"Menyalternativet startar <ulink url=\"hhttps://apps.kde.org/krename"
"\"><application>Krename</application></ulink>, ett mycket kraftfullt externt "
"verktyg för namnbyte."

#. Tag: title
#: menu-commands.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "Krename Features"
msgstr "Funktioner i Krename"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Renaming a list of files based on a set of expressions"
msgstr "Byt namn på en lista av filer baserat på en uppsättning uttryck"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copying/moving a list of files to another folder"
msgstr "Kopiera eller flytta en lista av filer till en annan katalog"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Convert filenames to upper/lower case"
msgstr "Konvertera filnamn till stora eller små bokstäver"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding numbers to filenames"
msgstr "Lägg till nummer i filnamn"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finding and replacing parts of the filename"
msgstr "Hitta och ersätt delar av filnamnet"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Renaming MP3/OGG Vorbis files based on their ID3 tags"
msgstr "Namnbyte av MP3- och OGG Vorbis-filer baserat på deras ID3-taggar"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting access and modification dates"
msgstr "Ändra åtkomst- och ändringsdatum"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing permissions and file ownership"
msgstr "Ändra behörigheter och filens ägare"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "A plugin API which allows you to extend KRename's features"
msgstr ""
"Ett programmeringsgränssnitt för insticksprogram som låter dig utöka "
"KRenames funktioner"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "Renaming folders recursively"
msgstr "Byt namn på kataloger rekursivt"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "Support for KFilePlugins"
msgstr "Stöd för Kfileplugins"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undo renaming"
msgstr "Ångra namnbyte"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "And many more...."
msgstr "Och mycket mer ..."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Create Checksum...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Skapa checksumma...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"checksum\">Checksum creation</link> on file(s) and/or "
"folder(s)."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"checksum\">Skapa checksummor</link> för filer och/eller "
"kataloger."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Verify Checksum...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Verifiera checksumma...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: link
#: menu-commands.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "Verify Checksum"
msgstr "Verifiera checksumma"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Split File...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dela fil...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"splitter\">Split file</link> function splits a file up "
"into multiple smaller files so that it can be stored on several smaller "
"media (like <hardware>diskettes, zip-drives, ...</hardware>) or sent by e-"
"mail."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen <link linkend=\"splitter\">Dela fil</link> delar upp en fil i "
"många mindre filer så att den kan lagras på flera mindre medier (som "
"<hardware>disketter, zip-enheter, ...</hardware>) eller skickas med e-post."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Combine Files...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kombinera filer...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"splitter\">Combine files</link> function combines "
"multiple files into one file after the <link linkend=\"splitter\">Split "
"file</link> function was used."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen <link linkend=\"splitter\">Kombinera filer</link> kombinerar "
"flera filer till en fil efter att funktionen <link linkend=\"splitter\">Dela "
"fil</link> har använts."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Avsluta</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Closes &krusader; and cleans up the temporary folder, the same as pressing "
"<keycap>F10</keycap> key."
msgstr ""
"Stänger &krusader; och rensar den tillfälliga katalogen. Samma sak som att "
"trycka på tangenten <keycap>F10</keycap>."

#. Tag: title
#: menu-commands.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Menu"
msgstr "Menyn Redigera"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Redigera</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Klipp ut</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"copying\">Cuts</link> the selected file(s) to the clipboard "
"to be moved to another location."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"copying\">Klipper ut</link> de markerade filerna till "
"klippbordet för att flyttas till en annan plats."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Redigera</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiera</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"copying\">Copies</link> the selected file(s) to the "
"clipboard to be moved to another location."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"copying\">Kopierar</link> markerade filer till klippbordet "
"för att flyttas till en annan plats."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Redigera</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Klistra in</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"copying\">Pastes</link> previously cut or copied items from "
"the clipboard to the current folder."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"copying\">Klistrar in</link> tidigare urklippta eller "
"kopierade objekt från klippbordet till den aktuella katalogen."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F8</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F8</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Redigera</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Ta bort</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"deleting\">Deletes</link> the currently selected file(s)."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"deleting\">Tar bort</link> filen eller filerna som för "
"närvarande är markerade."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>+</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select Group...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>+</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Redigera</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Markera grupp...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a dialog which allows you to select files in the active panel. In the "
"<guilabel>Search for</guilabel> dialog place the main search criteria. Enter "
"a filename, a wildcard ( <literal role=\"extension\">*.o.*</literal>, "
"<literal role=\"extension\">*.c</literal> &etc;) or both - separated by a "
"space. When using <literal>'text'</literal>, the results are the same as "
"<literal>'*text*'</literal>. You can exclude files from the search with "
"'|' (&eg; <literal role=\"extension\">'*.cpp *.h | *.moc.cpp'</literal>). "
"With the <link linkend=\"profiles\">profile handler</link> you can manage "
"your selections for future usage. A double-click on a profile is the same as "
"entering the selection and pressing the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button. "
"More options for <guilabel>Select Group</guilabel> dialog are explained in "
"the <link linkend=\"krusearcher\">Search dialog</link>, which are basically "
"almost the same dialogs."
msgstr ""
"Öppnar en dialogruta som låter dig markera filer i den aktiva panelen. Lägg "
"till huvudkriterierna för sökningen i dialogrutan <guilabel>Sök efter</"
"guilabel>. Skriv in ett filnamn, jokertecken (<literal role=\"extension\">*."
"o.*</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">*.c</literal>, etc.) eller båda, "
"åtskilda av mellanslag. När <literal>'text'</literal> används, är resultatet "
"samma som <literal>'*text*'</literal>. Du kan undanta filer från sökningen "
"med '|' (t.ex. <literal role=\"extension\">'*.cpp *.h | *.moc.cpp'</"
"literal>). Du kan hantera urval för framtida användning med <link linkend="
"\"profiles\">profilhanteraren</link>. Att dubbelklicka på en profil är samma "
"sak som att skriva in urvalet och klicka på knappen <guibutton>Ok</"
"guibutton>. Fler alternativ för dialogrutan <guilabel>Markera grupp</"
"guilabel> förklaras för <link linkend=\"krusearcher\">Sökdialogrutan</link>, "
"vilken egentligen är nästan samma dialogruta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>-</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Unselect Group...</"
"guimenuitem>"
